<i>noun</i>: 내야 [내ː야] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>내야 [내ː야]</dt><br>
<dd>1. infield</dd><br>
<dd>야구에서 본루, 일루, 이루, 삼루를 이은 선 안.</dd><br>
<dd>The area inside the line connecting the home base, first base, second base, and third base in baseball.</dd><br>
<dd>2. infield</dd><br>
<dd>내야를 수비하는 선수들.</dd><br>
<dd>Baseball players defending the infield.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>